---
title: Speedy Sesame-Teriyaki Tofu Bowls with Carrots and Edamame Rice
description: This tofu teriyaki on pillowy jasmine rice hits all the right notes: salty, sweet, filling and as spicy as you like it! But the best part? It all comes together in just 25 minutes!
